pointSchemas.name: Funding Rate (OI Weighted)
pointSchemas.description: The funding rate for the asset weighted by the open interest. This is expressed as a percentage, e.g. 0.01 = 1%.

pointSchemas.name: Funding Rate (Volume Weighted)
pointSchemas.description: The funding rate for the asset weighted by trading volume. This is expressed as a percentage, e.g. 0.01 = 1%.
